= UML =

http://maze-solver.googlecode.com/files/maze-model-interface-uml.png

The above diagram shows the UML for the Maze Model Interfaces. It is broken up into 2 parts, the getter methods and the setter methods. This allows an immutable reference of the model to be passed to code that should not be changing it.
